{"tid":995183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打人惹公憤　躁男MK遭圍毆昏迷","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T09:19:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1951d1fb5bbb2f1f4f3655997d839e79aa3e729","tid":995183,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190125/20598726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598726&d=9I4BeS4eQ9jGYJ6jP2Db654f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bab70e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598726&h=b49da56a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190125/20598726</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月25日 <br />\n<br />\n打人惹公憤　躁男MK遭圍毆昏迷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190125/large/a0705a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190125%2Flarge%2Fa0705a.gif&h=e73261a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名黑衣男昨於旺角街頭與送貨工人發生碰撞，竟出拳攻擊對方，更辱罵圍觀者，最終被四人圍毆，黑衣男被打至昏迷倒地，事後被送院救治，打人者事後不知去向。<br />\n<br />\n現場為旺角登打士街好景商場外，昨傍晚6時半，一名黑衣男推着載有狗隻的寵物車經過，與中年漢的送貨手推車碰撞，黑衣男情緒激動，大聲爆粗，更出手拍打中年漢頭部，對方只以手擋格及閃避，惟黑衣男得寸進尺，除揮拳狠擊，更起腳踢對方，其間中年漢解釋「係你自己行埋嚟」，黑衣男更怒斥：「你啲貨係死，我隻狗係生㗎！」更說：「報警吖！」<br />\n<br />\n其時，一名圍觀者上前問遇襲中年漢是否要驗傷和報警，豈料黑衣男意氣風發喝罵：「關你鬼事呀！」此時四名男子不值黑衣男所為，群起上前圍毆，黑衣男毫無還擊之力終倒地，復遭對方狂踩，中年漢其後離開。現場消息指黑衣男一度昏迷，救護員到場將33歲姓莫傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘婉玲  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n涉五度姦親女　父辯稱「淨係摸」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n機場廁所五塗大便　無業漢罰款"},{"pid":"8151b28a359c3f57aab307c6a4e19daf8ed2a45e","tid":995183,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"我係琴晚果隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人理我好肚餓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要食雞比"},{"pid":"08501902d3457b842ae56992f687abacd121beff","tid":995183,"uid":51171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"出黎行，唔好以為得自己可以惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次當買個教訓"}]}